==Tallast==
Tayrin n yan afrux (Izil) n yat fruxt (Tillili). Angal ar isawal fyat tayri li ifln Izil bla ixf issaɣs tayri issudan ignwan. Mac afruxad ar ismuqqul izd tayri yad tga ɣir z yat tasga, ar iẓrra masd Tillili ur as baḥra tkfa tizi ns wala tsmaqql gis. mayd af ra yamz graygat yan abrid llit issufɣn. 
Zrin wussan d isgwasn, sbadel afgan wala tiwuriwines, Izil rayg angmar ni islman, immurzm taggurt f tuwuriwin n il d iftasn d islman, ifl tiɣri wala ikrrajn. Tillili rast slkmn izdayn yaḍnin iy wis ngmas. Azday amaynu rad ifl i Tillili ɣalli mu ur tswingm. Ra ttassi aḥlig bla taḥl. Tamukristad tamaynut rast tsffaɣ tamazirt.
Afra liɣ ratswingm ig taɣarast liraddars iguru igat a trwl, twats dar Izil lli izdɣn ɣ yat tuzdɣt n izufriyn, imlas tiswak d iɣarasn yaḍnin.
